{"metadata":{"title":"OUDSTokensComponent","externalID":"OUDSTokensComponent","role":"collection","symbolKind":"module","modules":[{"name":"OUDSTokensComponent"}],"roleHeading":"Framework"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"These ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"tokens","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" are defined for components and refer to semantic tokens or raw tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"They can be seen as a kind of bridge between components and in the end primitive values of the design kit.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Thus if a component need to change for example its "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"background color"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":", and if a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"component token","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" is used for it, then only the value of this "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"token"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" should be changed without any modification on the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"component","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" definition."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Components","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" use "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" exposed through the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" thanks to token providers to get their style values."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components tokens are defined and gathered inside "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift protocol"}]},{"text":" so as to be exposed then through implementation of ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" thanks to dedicated tokens providers."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Because we choose to split responsabilities and objects into their own modules, we faced troubles to make possible for children themes or providers to override properties declared in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"protocols"}]},{"text":" and defined in ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"extensions","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"That is the reason why tokens are exposed as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@objc open"},{"text":" to be available and overridable anywhere.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Example with "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Declare some component tokens for buttons with properties they must apply","public protocol ButtonComponentTokens {","    var buttonSizeMaxHeight: SizeSemanticToken { get }","    var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { get }","    var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { get }","    var buttonColorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { get }","    var buttonSpacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { get }","}","","\/\/ There is an existing provider for such tokens","open class OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider { }","","\/\/ Define the components tokens exposed through the theme thanks to provider","extension OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider: ButtonComponentTokens {","","    \/\/ Raw tokens can be used","","    @objc open var buttonSizeMaxHeight: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.dimension600 }","    ","    \/\/ And also semantic tokens","","    @objc open var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.borderWidthThicker }","    @objc open var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.borderRadiusMedium }","    @objc open var buttonColorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.colorRepositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","    @objc open var buttonSpacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.spacePaddingInlineSpacious }","}","","\/\/ This provider is then exposed through OUDSTheme as an AllButtonComponentTokensProvider"]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Component-tokens-management","level":2,"text":"Component tokens management"},{"text":"How to add component tokens","anchor":"How-to-add-component-tokens","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"First, you need to define which from family this semantic comes, such tokens are strongly related to components.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If your token is not from one of the existing groups, maybe you should redesign your token or create a new family.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"To do that, you will have to create a dedicated Swift "},{"code":"protocol","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", with a useful name, and declare as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"var"},{"type":"text","text":" the component token."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If you already know the family, just update the matching files.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"How to update or remove component tokens","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"How-to-update-or-remove-component-tokens"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Quite simple, find the component token you want to update or remove, and update or remove it.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"But beware, if you change the name of the property or if you move it from a ","type":"text"},{"code":"protocol","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to another, or if you remove the token, you must keep retrocompatibility as much as possible so as to avoid to break any public API. Keep also the CHANGELOG and\/or the release updated with some BREAKING CHANGE notification, and also the Git history clean."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you update the value, keep also the CHANGELOG and\/or RELEASE NOTE updated so as to let your users know the variables have been changed.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"About-tests-of-tokens","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"About tests of tokens"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When component tokens have been added, removed or renamed, unit tests must be updated.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"We do not test the component tokens values as they are, because these values will be generated and keeping up to date the unit tests may be time wasting.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"But for each component tokens we check if a subtheme can override the token using derived tokens providers.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"How to use component tokens","type":"heading","anchor":"How-to-use-component-tokens"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In fact, the component tokens are declared and gathered in ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift protocol","type":"text"}]},{"text":" so as to force any theme to implement them, and also to allow any theme to expose such properties whathever the implementation of the theme is, across providers.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Because ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens"}]},{"text":" have for values ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"raw tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"semantic tokens"}]},{"text":", and in the end for values primitive types, and all these tokens are declared with ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"type aliases"}]},{"text":" refering all together, you can handle a ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component token"}]},{"type":"text","text":" directly in your view because the final value will be used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Thus, get the theme and call the needed property with some helpers.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["struct SomeView: View {","","    @Environment(\\.theme) private var theme \/\/ Supposed you used in your root view the `OUDSThemeableView` to register the theme","    @Environment(\\.colorScheme) private var colorScheme","","    var body: some View {","        Button {","            \/\/ Some action","        } label: {","            Text(\"Some label\")","                .cornerRadius(theme.button.buttonBorderRadius)","        }","        .padding(.leading, theme.button.buttonSpacePaddingInlineArrowStart)","        .padding(.trailing, theme.button.buttonSpacePaddingInlineArrowEnd)","        .background(theme.button.buttonColorBgStrongEnabledMono)","        .overlay(","            RoundedRectangle(cornerRadius: theme.button.buttonBorderRadius)","                .stroke(Color.blue, lineWidth: theme.button.buttonBorderWidthDefault)","        )","    }","\/*","    - The theme provides border semantic tokens \"buttonBorderRadius\" and \"buttonBorderWidthDefault\"","    - The theme provides a color semantic token \"buttonColorBgStrongEnabledMono\"","    - The theme provides spaces semantic token \"buttonSpacePaddingInlineArrowStart\" and \"buttonSpacePaddingInlineArrowEnd\"","*\/","}","","\/\/ Do not forget in your app to use the `OUDSThemeableView` for your theme, e.g. `OrangeTheme`","@main","struct DesignToolbox: App {","","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","                ...","            }","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudstokenscomponent"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/LinkComponentTokens","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/SelectComponentTokens","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/SkeletonComponentTokens","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/TagComponentTokens"],"title":"Group","anchor":"Group"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/AllButtonComponentTokensProvider"],"anchor":"Type-Aliases","generated":true,"title":"Type Aliases"}],"references":{"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent/documentation/OUDSTokensComponent/ButtonComponentTokens":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Declares all component tokens for buttons components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSButton"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Use for tokens providers like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens","url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenscomponent\/buttoncomponenttokens","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ButtonComponentTokens"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ButtonComponentTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"ButtonComponentTokens","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent/documentation/OUDSTokensComponent/AllButtonComponentTokensProvider":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/AllButtonComponentTokensProvider","title":"AllButtonComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"typealias","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AllButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"AllButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type alias only for "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to keep consistency with other type aliases"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"merging several protocols.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" matches this type alias.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenscomponent\/allbuttoncomponenttokensprovider","kind":"symbol"},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent/documentation/OUDSTokensComponent/TagComponentTokens":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenscomponent\/tagcomponenttokens","title":"TagComponentTokens","abstract":[{"text":"Declares all component tokens for tags components like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTag","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Use for tokens providers like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"TagComponentTokens"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"TagComponentTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/TagComponentTokens","kind":"symbol"},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent/documentation/OUDSTokensComponent/SelectComponentTokens":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SelectComponentTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"SelectComponentTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"SelectComponentTokens","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/SelectComponentTokens","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Declares all component tokens for links components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSelect"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Use for tokens providers like "},{"code":"OrangeThemeSelectComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenscomponent\/selectcomponenttokens","type":"topic"},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent/documentation/OUDSTokensComponent":{"title":"OUDSTokensComponent","url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenscomponent","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent","type":"topic","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"These "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"tokens","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" are defined for components and refer to semantic tokens or raw tokens."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"They can be seen as a kind of bridge between components and in the end primitive values of the design kit.","type":"text"}]},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent/documentation/OUDSTokensComponent/SkeletonComponentTokens":{"kind":"symbol","title":"SkeletonComponentTokens","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Declares all component tokens for links components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSkeleton"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Use for tokens providers like "},{"code":"OrangeThemeSkeletonComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/SkeletonComponentTokens","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SkeletonComponentTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SkeletonComponentTokens"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenscomponent\/skeletoncomponenttokens","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent/documentation/OUDSTokensComponent/LinkComponentTokens":{"title":"LinkComponentTokens","url":"\/documentation\/oudstokenscomponent\/linkcomponenttokens","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/LinkComponentTokens","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Declares all component tokens for links components like "},{"code":"OUDSLink","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Use for tokens providers like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"LinkComponentTokens"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"LinkComponentTokens"}],"kind":"symbol"}}}